    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712420/extras/21e2d9d87ace0253ce12bdb3e30fb815.avif?t=1641567122\" width=600 height=142 /></span><br><br>This is the life of Ralph, a teenage raccoon, in this story you will experience the most incredible moments of his life.<br>In this relaxing experience, accompany Ralph, his friends, his girlfriend and his family, in moments that we've all had as a teenager, featuring 5 amazing scenes in this puzzle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712420/extras/b0a24f3dfedc119d2be2717bbf6643bc.avif?t=1641567122\" width=600 height=81 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Engage in moments to feel peaceful and tranquil.<br></li><li> Handmade beautiful and relax with an immersive and unique trail.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712420/extras/701bacba52028a57efd52e66e48cdcea.avif?t=1641567122\" width=600 height=81 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> A game for everyone from difficult levels.<br></li><li> Features include zooming the scene, highlighting the pieces from the edge, shuffling the remaining pieces, previewing the scene.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712420/extras/51ba06d0e28d9f867023de11a761e3d3.avif?t=1641567122\" width=600 height=81 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Complete the puzzle and unlock the downloadable image.<br></li><li> Use it as your desktop background to inspire your day!<br></li><li> Play if you love cute animals or love puzzles ❤! </li></ul>",
